bd41abed01daf6d91c885353499459be32f3da","tid":1327533,"uid":96778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T07:17:44.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"c396c7007e206ab5a28966715a5df9cc1641bee4","tid":1327533,"uid":20160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d45943920d0592cc9726562f3663d4781dbf468c","tid":1327533,"uid":96778,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e6be12449c000d781029b778a23af08df2e4084e","tid":1327533,"uid":20160,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"9bb6cf6c2f77e42abc8e1dc1b0cbc6ed9a857f67","tid":1327533,"uid":96778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T16:18:42.000Z","msg":"我諗住9月去飛呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nChing介唔介意講你跟邊間學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/rrrrul\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Frrrrul&d=yxFCeCsiIqqjoL8q9QcQshyAur%2Bbp9MVyOkMM5%2FMxDY%3D&h=f805da91\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/rrrrul</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T06:39:30.000Z","msg":"咁係邊飛要諗既係<br />\n1.安全, 2. 天氣, 3. 學習環境 (like instructor/ school reputation/ airport 忙唔忙咁), 4. 錢<br />\n咁另外都可以諗下有冇話咩機特別想飛 e.g DA40<br />\n亦都可以諗下想學 d 咩例如 basic maneuver , stall, circuit 果 d <br />\n<br />\n咁諗完上面 d concern 再 google 下<br />\n<br />\n例如 melbourne 咁, 9月天氣未必咁穩定, rainfall 係全年黎講比較多, cloudbase 可能會低<br />\n咁就未必飛到, 因為初初學飛係飛 vfr, visibility, cloudbase 全部係 concern<br />\n<br />\nEnjoy and safe flight <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T07:16:24.000Z","msg":"Thank you 巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n天氣方面都有考慮過，始終9月個邊天氣都唔係幾穩定，但係因為我得呢個period有時間飛所以想博下有幾日天氣好可以飛<br />\n機種就諗住學DA40既，想學下basic操作，嘗試下揸飛機既感覺<br />\n揀melbourne就係因為我個邊有朋友所以可以慳住宿同租車錢，同埋時間都flexible 啲。本身諗住跟learn to fly但係google見佢聲譽麻麻地，其他flying school就未聽過/冇得就咁飛5-10個鐘，所以上嚟問下有冇巴絲飛過LTF以外既flying school既經驗"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T08:00:04.000Z","msg":"9月一定要 MEL, 天氣要搏既機會高 d 冇計<br />\n咁又係返返去 primary objective, 錢擺 priority 第幾位<br />\n如果唔係太 top priority 唔洗 limit 係1個城市<br />\n<br />\n另外要睇學校個 plane/ instructor slot, 係咪咁容易有 back up, 如果 popular, 咁 even 好天氣又未必有 slot 俾你 (因爲有機會同一日朝早飛到, 下午飛唔到)<br />\n<br />\n揀完地區之後就真係逐間聯絡 compare, quote 價... 好多都有得飛幾個鐘但要自己問<br />\n<br />\nJust a personal advise: 機型擺最後考慮, 任何1部 training aircraft like C172, DA20, piper pa28 都會俾到飛既感覺你, analog cockpit 會易 d 上手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nP.s. 安全永遠第一 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3dafe3d3a2fbe050617d6dfd89372f32752baec","tid":1327533,"uid":170268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T10:41:53.000Z","msg":"Pushhh 係Melbourne住 我都想知學邊間好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d936853996832f76274027f12da7c4809406fee1","tid":1327533,"uid":96778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c396c7007e206ab5a28966715a5df9cc1641bee4","tid":1327533,"uid":20160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d45943920d0592cc9726562f3663d4781dbf468c","tid":1327533,"uid":96778,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e6be12449c000d781029b778a23af08df2e4084e","tid":1327533,"uid":20160,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T06:39:30.000Z","msg":"咁係邊飛要諗既係<br />\n1.安全, 2. 天氣, 3. 學習環境 (like instructor/ school reputation/ airport 忙唔忙咁), 4. 錢<br />\n咁另外都可以諗下有冇話咩機特別想飛 e.g DA40<br />\n亦都可以諗下想學 d 咩例如 basic maneuver , stall, circuit 果 d <br />\n<br />\n咁諗完上面 d concern 再 google 下<br />\n<br />\n例如 melbourne 咁, 9月天氣未必咁穩定, rainfall 係全年黎講比較多, cloudbase 可能會低<br />\n咁就未必飛到, 因為初初學飛係飛 vfr, visibility, cloudbase 全部係 concern<br />\n<br />\nEnjoy and safe flight <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T07:16:24.000Z","msg":"Thank you 巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"